  "texts": [
    "We refer the reader to [22, 65] for further reading.",
    "However, we remark that the \"lifted\" HJB (1.6) is new in the framework of a general Hilbert space H. Literature: case H = R d.",
    "The study of controlled particle systems when H = R d and, especially, the problem of convergence of their value functions u n to a value function V of a control problem in the space of measures have attracted considerable attention in recent years.",
    "In particular, convergence results for the case of idiosyncratic noise were obtained in [71] (see also [11, 21, 56, 59, 60] for earlier and related results, including large deviations), and for the case of common noise in [48].",
    "For related problems, see also the recent papers [19, 44]."
